      "description": "Marcel's split soul, Clemar, enters the camera to freeze the moment. Marcel's Basic Attacks deal 50 (+40% Total Physical Attack) (+40% Total Magic Defense) (+40% Total Physical Defense) Physical Damage (cannot Crit). He cannot benefit from extra Attack Speed. Extra HP is converted into 1.5% Hybrid Defense.\nClemar automatically snaps photos of enemy heroes near Marcel, causing a brief Frozen Moment and dealing 20 (+5% their Max HP) True Damage (triggers Attack Effects). It also grants a shield of the same value to Marcel and a nearby allied hero. Cooldown: 12s per target (each Basic Attack from Marcel reduces this cooldown by 1s).",
